        "TileImage": "$($repository 9454339d-8f29-4ae6-97f4-96523a48bf08).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rYour target is Carlton Smith, a former ICA agent who has gone rogue, diverting Agency funds into illicit high-stakes poker games. This breach threatens our integrity. Terminate Smith and erase all traces of his actions. A hostage may possess sensitive knowledge, and another  missing agent has resurfaced as a pirate. Both are expendable.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
